Shaping the climate debate and policy Siemens is part of a number of platforms and initiatives that

allow us to participate in the debate on climate-related issues. For example, as part of the UN Global Compact Peer-Learning Group, we are sharing knowledge and lessons learned on various climate-related topics with other companies.

